examples.en: The floor was vibrating to the beat of the music.
The number of scholars vibrates from 20 to 90.
examples.ru: Число ученых колеблется от 20 до 90 человек.

examples.en: Long pendulums vibrate more slowly than short ones.

examples.en: A pendulum which will vibrate seconds in a true manner.
